{
  "stem": "27509.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever the nature of the city was, it was to some degree agrarian in the sense of structures of-- of the types of-- yes, there were certain parts of streets where-- or certain streets which were more elaborate and more expensive and more exclusive.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by and large, it-- the differences in living standards, with few exceptions, were reasonably average.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was Kupiecka, and like other streets of that nature.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because on one end, Kupiecka touched on-- on-- on Pilsudkiego, which was one of the two major streets of the city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our neighbors--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to work very hard, apart from the policeman, the postman, and on a-- and the-- and the-- and the man who looked after the-- the-- the-- the-- the house-- the-- the housing generally, as a sort of a caretaker, which in our case it did not apply.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But where there are bigger-- bigger number of flats, there was a caretaker in-- everything was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out of the 100,000 people, 70,000 were Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when I say 100,000, it was-- or-- it was including the outer laying fringes of the city, which were included into-- or just tacked onto the city itself for political reasons by the-- by the Polish authorities.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if you would have taken the city as-- on its own, the factor, it would have been 90% Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they added on the-- the fringes of the city, which were already peasantry and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the mix and the-- and the ratio between the Jewish people and the non-Jewish people at least was somewhere alleviated to only 2/3 out of-- of almost 100%.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember-- of course, I remember Father's mother who lived with us, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was Bobe.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
